cell.text:
H1
: Board size has a positive association with ESG performance in the logistics sector.

H2
: Board gender diversity has a positive association with ESG performance in the logistics sector.
Accepted for composite ESG score and Governance Pillar

H3
: Board independence has a positive association with ESG performance in the logistics sector.

H4
: CEO and board chair separation has a positive association with ESG performance in the logistics sector.

H5
: The existence of a sustainability committee (i.e., CSR) has a positive association with ESG performance in the logistics sector.
Accepted for composite ESG score and Social Pillar

H6
: Ownership diffusion has a positive association with ESG performance in the logistics sector.

H7
